id: VAL-mission-002-boundary-pattern
kind: validation
name: Mission 002 — boundary pattern, full success
status: draft
description: Gemma 4 E2B completes a clockwise boundary pattern mission (4 waypoints) with 4/4 correct decisions and autonomous RTL at mission completion. Demonstrates that the V1.0 architecture meets the visual grounding and explainability needs: the model reasons from the map image, maintains continuity via the scratchpad, and the reasoning log is coherent and accurate post-flight.
validates: NEED-explainable-decisions, NEED-visual-grounding
scope: CMP-mission-computer
method: demonstration
executions: 1
latest_outcome: passed
